reviewText: You'll see a dynamite Swede who sings up a storm, plays every instrument you can imagine, and is a ball to watch. (I'm sure Region 2 are available, so before buying a used copy, I'd contact the seller and get him to agree to your returning it if it doesn't play.) AMZN should check with Carling Records Jazzart Sweeden AB and make sure new inventory will play Region 1. My guess is that this is all-regions, but it doesn't say so. It was recorded in Boras in 2012, the visuals are bit fuzzy but the sound is fine. Lots of fun!
